---
// Projects section component
---

<section id="proyectos" class="max-w-4xl mx-auto my-16 p-8 bg-gradient-to-t from-gray-200 via-gray-300 via-green-200 via-green-400 to-green-600 bg-fixed rounded-xl shadow-lg shadow-black/25 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-green-700/50 transition-shadow duration-300 scroll-mt-20">
  <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8 text-green-900 drop-shadow-sm">Proyectos</h3>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
    <!-- Proyecto 1: Landing Pages -->
    <div class="bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6 border border-white/30 hover:bg-white/30 transition-all duration-300">
      <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-green-900">Landing Pages Modernas</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-800 mb-4">Desarrollo de páginas de aterrizaje responsivas con Astro y Tailwind CSS, optimizadas para conversión y experiencia de usuario.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full text-sm">Astro</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full text-sm">Tailwind CSS</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-orange-600 text-white rounded-full text-sm">HTML</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Proyecto 2: API Valorant -->
    <div class="bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6 border border-white/30 hover:bg-white/30 transition-all duration-300">
      <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-green-900">Integración API Valorant</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-800 mb-4">Aplicación web que consume la API de Valorant para mostrar estadísticas de jugadores y datos del juego en tiempo real.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-yellow-600 text-white rounded-full text-sm">JavaScript</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full text-sm">API REST</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full text-sm">JSON</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Proyecto 3: Sistema de Gestión -->
    <div class="bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6 border border-white/30 hover:bg-white/30 transition-all duration-300">
      <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-green-900">Sistema de Gestión de Inventario</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-800 mb-4">Aplicación completa para la gestión de inventarios con CRUD completo, autenticación y reportes.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full text-sm">Python</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full text-sm">MongoDB</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-red-600 text-white rounded-full text-sm">Flask</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Proyecto 4: Sistema Veterinaria -->
    <div class="bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6 border border-white/30 hover:bg-white/30 transition-all duration-300">
      <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-green-900">Sistema de Veterinaria</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-800 mb-4">Plataforma web para gestión de citas, historial médico de mascotas y administración de clientes veterinarios.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-yellow-600 text-white rounded-full text-sm">JavaScript</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full text-sm">Node.js</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full text-sm">MongoDB</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-center mt-8">
    <p class="text-gray-800 mb-4">¿Quieres ver más proyectos?</p>
    <a
      href="https://github.com/Deamacevedo"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gray-900 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors duration-300"
    >
      <img src="/src/assets/icons/github_light.svg" alt="GitHub" class="w-5 h-5" />
      Ver en GitHub
    </a>
  </div>
</section>